---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Summary</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Equipped with over 3 years of education in software development and possessing a deep understanding of programming languages including Java and Python. Proficient in web development with a knack for both back-end and front-end development. Seeking a full-time software developer internship to gain practical experience and further cultivate skills sector.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Digital Operations Specialist at Moore Hearing Clinic"
      subtitle="From 2015 to Present, Ottumwa, IA"
    >
      <div>
        <ul class="list-disc">
          <li>Established, maintained, and updated the company website, enhancing the clinic's online presence by doubling website traffic.</li>
          <li>Managed the clinic's social media platforms, successfully increasing engagement through targeted content strategies.</li>
          <li>Oversaw insurance filings for over 150 patients annually, streamlining the process.</li>
          <li>Designed and implemented new customer information and audiology forms, improving the data collection process.</li>
          <li>Initiated and grew a mailing list from scratch to over 200 active subscribers, enhancing communication and engagement with clients.</li>
          <li>Developed a Python program to automate insurance calculations, reducing processing time by 50% and minimizing errors.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Indian Hills Community College"
      subtitle="Expected August 2023, Computer Software Development, A.A.S, Ottumwa, IA"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Iowa State University"
      subtitle="2019 to 2021, Computer Science, Ames, IA"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>React</li>
    <li>NextJS</li>
    <li>Java</li>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>TypeScript</li>
    <li>JavaScript</li>
    <li>Cobol</li>
    <li>C#</li>
    <li>GitHub</li>
    <li>Agile</li>
    <li>Scrum</li>
    <li>Flask</li>
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>Tailwind</li>
    <li>Bootstrap</li>
    <li>Spring</li>
    <li>MySQL</li>
    <li>PostgreSQL</li>
    <li>Blazor</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
